parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can lead to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates without input from the driver
the accelerator pedal sticks to the floor
the vehicle surges forward
and the engine RPM increases unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Accelerator pedal issues can lead to unintended acceleration, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The accelerator pedal feels soft or spongy
the pedal sticks to the floor
the pedal does not return to its normal position
and the pedal has a delayed return to its normal position.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Cruise control malfunction can lead to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The cruise control stops working
the cruise control light is illuminated but the system does not function
and the steering column is related to the issue.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine performance issues can lead to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The engine exhibits abnormal behavior
such as high RPM
shaking
and loss of power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Recall repair issues can lead to continued safety risks and accidents.
symptoms: The recall repair did not correct the failure
the dealer did not provide a timely appointment
and the repair did not address the underlying issue.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake pedal interference can lead to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The floor mat interferes with the brake pedal
restricting the driver's ability to press the pedal fully.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rusting of the frame and bed can cause the bed to detach from the frame while driving, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: Rusting of the frame
bed
and surrounding areas
including the bed bolts
fuel tank straps
and rear bumper. Visible signs of rust
such as bubbling or flaking paint
and holes in the bed floor.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The premature failure of the paint and clear coat can lead to rusting and corrosion, compromising the structural integrity of the vehicle.
symptoms: Chipping
flaking
or bubbling of the paint and clear coat
especially on the hood and top of the truck. Visible signs of rust or corrosion under the paint.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corrosion of the brake lines and frame can cause brake failure, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: Rusted or corroded brake lines
frame
and surrounding areas. Visible signs of rust or corrosion
such as holes or flaking metal.
